effective reproduction number in mid March as testing
started to reveal very high numbers of unrecorded cases
prevalent in the population. The first day with significant
number of tests was 13 March (2,900, compared to a previous
high of 44). Estimates of R, based on a sliding 7 day
window, cannot be taken regarded as useful until 20 March
